summary: Hey babylumps I was wondering if you'd do me the honor of shipping me with a kpop idol or 4. Can I get them for, Monsta X,...
body:
Hey babylumps I was wondering if you’d do me the honor of shipping me with a kpop idol or 4. Can I get them for, Monsta X, Seventeen, Got 7, and BTS (I hope that’s not too many I couldn’t get to your guidelines for some odd reason, the first 3 if it too much) PS. also if there’s a way to, can you exclude my pictures I’m kind of extremely shy/self-conscious thanks bunny

  • ship for @hotheauxworld
  • Hello sweetie! 4 groups is perfectly fine :) that’s the maximum. And don’t be ashamed because you are so mf pretty like you’re glowing girl😻love ya❤️

In Monsta X, I ship you with… I.M!

In Seventeen, I ship you with… Jun!

In Got7, I ship you with… Bambam!

In BTS, I ship you with… Taehyung!

Between all of them, I ship you with I.M the most. I hope that you like your ships and got your biases! Have a nice day/night and feel free to request more.🧡
